1.name: Modulate
1.desc: Some monsters show notes only on the right beats and show question mark notes the rest of the time.

2.name: Note: White Flash
2.desc: Play Note: White Flash at the right time to defeat the blue note monster, damaging it on the corresponding beat. Perfect timing will deal critical DMG. When a measure contains two or more Notes: White Flash, the next Note: White Flash will be Perfectly Harmonious, chasing on the fourth beat.

5.name: Variation: Relationship Echo
5.desc: After playing the note, Izanami will gain Energy. She loses Energy if you play a wrong note. When her Energy is full, she enters Relationship Echo mode. With each followup strike, Hisame attacks along with Izanami.

6.name: Legato
6.desc: Some monsters get an additional echo note when they get notes. You must input an extra note to defeat them.
